		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You whisper a spell that shields you and your allies from being detected from your target, forcing their mind to ignore details of your presence.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save int]]{Intelligence Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[charmed] by you. While charmed in this way, your target is unable to perceive any creature you choose to hide from them. Your target also cannot otherwise detect their presence, and may seem to be deliberately oblivious. Target rolls save again at the end of each of their turns, ending effect on success.</p><p>The effect ends for a target if you or a creature you've hidden take hostile action against the target.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target three additional creatures for each spell level above 5th.</p>",
